<para>
  An <link
  linkend="Section-Concepts-Microstructure-OrientationMap"><classname>Orientation
  Map</classname></link> specifies the orientation of the crystalline
  axes at every point in a &micro;.  This menu contains commands for
  manipulating <classname>Orientation Maps</classname>.
</para>
<para>
  There is no <link linkend="Chapter-Tasks">Task Page</link> devoted
  to orientation maps. The commands are in the menu bar of the main
  &oof2; window.
</para>


